## 5. Ownership

The Software operates under a three-tier ownership model:

(a) MANAGED TIER
Files distributed as part of the Software (e.g., `.claude/sdlc/`,
including framework hooks, rules, and skills) are the intellectual
property of ngentiq and are licensed, not sold.

(b) CUSTOMER TIER
Configurations, agents, rules, skills, and other artifacts created by
or for a customer (e.g., `.claude/PROJECT-RULES.md`, customer-authored
agents under `.claude/agents/`, project `CLAUDE.md`) are the exclusive
property of that customer. No rights are claimed by ngentiq over such
content.

(c) USER TIER
Personal settings and local configurations (e.g.,
`.claude/settings.local.json`) are the exclusive property of the
individual user. No rights are claimed by ngentiq.

